      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROMAN PARTY (2) is a handy type who was well below best latest at this track, finishing fourth (22.55) in a Grade 5. Normally fast to begin but shuffled back last time. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Better than last start and worth following up. FLYING BLOSSOM (1) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (22.25) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Can find the frame this time. MONTEBELLO (7) finds it hard to break through. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (22.25) at this track. Yet to miss the placings from three starts out of this box. Can measure up. BOOM SMACKING (3) was a surprise last-start placegetter who is in the mix again.",
